OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSoldier reunited with girl 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhe met in France in WW2    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, For almost 80 years, Reg Pye had her   
OL,6, photograph in his wallet.              
OL,8,FHuguette left the picture in Reg's van 
OL,9,Fas thanks for sharing a jam sandwich   
OL,10,Fwith her while he waited to advance    
OL,11,Finto France as World War Two raged.    
OL,13,FA chance encounter amid the horrors of 
OL,14,Fwar near the Normandy beaches and just 
OL,15,Fweeks after D-Day may have been brief, 
OL,16,Fbut the memory has lasted a lifetime.  
OL,18,FSo much so that veteran Reg, 99, wanted
OL,19,Fto meet again - and they have in an    
OL,20,Femotional rendezvous 78 years later.   
